monton, but the track is called \"Law Bent\" .',NULL,NULL),(64572,3686,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/29/Volunteer Playlist - September 29, 2023 at 20:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-29 20:00:00',86507648,'2023-12-04 10:06:44',NULL,'The UM team wants to know what people are up to when it comes to the COVID pandemic. They\'re looking for people who are between the ages of 5 and 65. They want to know how they\'re disrupting the world in ways that make the world less safe. You can find out more about the UM team by visiting their website or by following them on Twitter.',NULL,NULL),(64573,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Reconciliation - September 30, 2022 at 18:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2022-09-30 18:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-30 02:08:15',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64574,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Reconciliation - September 30, 2022 at 17:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2022-09-30 17:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-30 02:08:15',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64575,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Reconciliation - September 30, 2022 at 16:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2022-09-30 16:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-30 02:08:16',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64576,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Reconciliation - September 30, 2022 at 15:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2022-09-30 15:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-30 02:08:16',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64577,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Reconciliation - September 30, 2022 at 14:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2022-09-30 14:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-30 02:08:17',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64578,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Reconciliation - September 30, 2022 at 13:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2022-09-30 13:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-30 02:08:18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64579,14544,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2022/09/30/National Day for Truth and Rec