colate raspberry brownies, almond tart, bread and butter, pastry pudding and custard, Portuguese custard tarts and blondes. They talk about how cool the place is and how they\'re roasting coffee.',NULL,NULL),(67324,180,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/8hc7su/HOWL_OCTOBER_24_20237mm2e.mp3','2023-10-25 13:23:25',56714472,'2023-11-18 10:53:01',NULL,'In this episode, the narrator announces that he has not received many submissions for a \"Halloween-themed open mic\" to be held on the 31st of October, 2023. Instead, he is giving readers until tomorrow, the 25th of October to submit their \"spooky\" poems to him.\n\nIn this interview, he introduces his first guest, Paola Ferrantes, who has won several awards for her short fiction and poetry. She is a writer who is living with depression and is known for her \"complex\" stories. Her book, \"What to Wear When surviving a lion attack,\" is a collection of her short stories and is described as \"a lot of intricate Sci-fi and Horror stories in there.\n\n\" Her book is described by the narrator as being \"for movie fans of course\" and \"for book fans like myself.\" The narrator explains that the book\'s title, \"Her body among animals,\" stems from the fact that \"there are animals in her body.\" He explains that he does not believe that a book can be judged by its cover alone, but by its \"body among animals.\" The title of his book, he says, \"was a way of saying that the stories in it were about animals.\" He',NULL,NULL),(67330,80,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/25/CFRU Playlist - October 25, 2023 at 07:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-25 07:00:00',86638720,'2023-10-25 14:06:10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(67331,78,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/25/Morning Soul Shake-Up! - October 25, 2023 at 08:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-25 08:00:00',86507648,'2023-11-18 10:43:16',NULL,'',NULL,NULL),(67335,159,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/g24utc/CAREER_-_CareerBuzzCIUTfinaloctober2520237hroq.mp3','2023-10-25 15:30:00',846700