ars. He\'s asking people to send him an email. He also wants people to call the phone room. He needs volunteers to help him with the phone booth. Beef Farmer is taking the band on as well. Richard asks everyone to go to the charity site to make donations. It\'s so easy to do.',NULL,NULL),(69430,186,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/jz7pih/November_16th_2023_Higher_Ground6k6ep.mp3','2023-11-20 16:29:27',287962512,'2023-11-21 01:45:10','2023-11-20 17:05:37','The Higher Ground Show is a fundraiser for the community radio station, CIUT. Higher Ground is a show that mixes music from the great reverend Evo Taylor and other great artists.\n\nThe show is hosted by the station\'s founder and executive producer, David Macpherson. He has been doing the show for 25 years and feels that it is important for the listeners of the station. He tells listeners that the station relies on their support not the support of big corporations. He reminds listeners that CIUT is their home and that all the music on the show is from their community. He urges listeners to join the station and to give a bit of money so that the show can continue. \n\nIf you are just tuning in, the show invites you to come and support the station, which is located in the heart of the city. If you have not yet done so, please visit the station to make your contribution. You can pay by going to the website and clicking on the \"donate\" button on the top right hand corner. There, you will find a link to the show where you can pay for the show. The station hopes that listeners will continue to listen to it and support it',NULL,NULL),(69431,206,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/jb83n8/November_18th_2023_The_Minx_Sessionsazqmn.mp3','2023-11-20 15:54:59',287962512,'2023-11-20 23:04:09','2023-11-20 17:05:50','',NULL,NULL),(69432,216,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/5xusmv/RAW111723.mp3','2023-11-20 16:07:56',287962512,'2023-11-21 01:23:15','2023-11-20 17:05:53','',NULL,NULL),(69433,216,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/6ebq